868
00:58:47,877 --> 00:58:48,942
<font color="yellow">Aku kan bukan mempelainya.</font>

869
00:58:48,942 --> 00:58:53,197
<font color="yellow">Kita kan harus berfoto besok.</font>

870
00:58:59,871 --> 00:59:03,496
<font color="yellow">Aku mau ke supermarket.
