878
00:59:31,440 --> 00:59:32,949
<font color="yellow"><i>Hei, Shin Se Young.</i></font>

879
00:59:34,799 --> 00:59:36,659
<font color="yellow">Apa dia sibuk?</font>

880
00:59:36,659 --> 00:59:38,474
<font color="yellow">Atau dia marah karena sesuatu?</font>

881
00:59:38,474 --> 00:59:41,063
<font color="yellow">Dia bahkan tidak mau menunjukkan wajahnya padaku.
